<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFB56A0AF7FB947E173FB807" pageId="78" pageNumber="836" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFB56A0AF7FB947E1438B942" blockId="78.[2052,2649,551,979]" pageId="78" pageNumber="836">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFB56A0AF7FB947E169FB97A" bold="true" box="[2055,2207,551,584]" pageId="78" pageNumber="836">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB56A0AF743947E17D3B97A" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1914" box="[2239,2515,551,584]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pharotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="78" pageNumber="836" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="imogene">Ia io Thomas, 1902</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="74FC3CA3FFB56A0AF610947E1438B942" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3783319526" pageId="78" pageNumber="836">
“Chung Yang [= Chung-yang], S. Hupeh, 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFB56A0AF62D94161425B942" box="[2513,2597,591,624]" name="China" pageId="78" pageNumber="836">China</collectingCountry>
.”
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFB56A0AF7F4942F173FB807" blockId="78.[2052,2649,551,979]" pageId="78" pageNumber="836">
Ia is sister to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB56A0AF72F942F175EB9A5" authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1875" box="[2259,2398,630,663]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotomanes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="78" pageNumber="836" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Scotomanes</taxonomicName>
within Eptesicini based on phylogenetic data. It has been considered a subgenus of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB56A0AF677949C1413B9D4" authorityName="Kaup" authorityYear="1829" box="[2443,2579,709,742]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="78" pageNumber="836" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Pipistrellus</taxonomicName>
, but the two genera are not closely related. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
